==Ice hockey affiliations==
The UMAC does not sponsor ice hockey. Two UMAC member schools sponsor men&#x27;s and women&#x27;s ice hockey as a varsity sport. Northland College and UW-Superior are members of the Wisconsin Intercollegiate Athletic Conference.

